snippet.title: Retro Map Jam 5: The Windtunnels, part 2 FINAL
snippet.description:
"Tricky Bricks" by Qmaster, "Deterritorialization" by Shambler, "Good Map, Pipe Dreams" by Shamblernaut, and "Bethel Ekon-Lin" by Tens

Played on Quakespasm, and recorded with OBS over Youtube Gaming!

https://www.quaddicted.com/reviews/retrojam5.html

I’m playin’ this blind! Lets stare at some walls!

This series of WAD's contain some solid levels! 

---

This is a slow-paced "Let Play" with little commentary.
